{"tid":110646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑港錶行太子爺炫耀飯局　曝光內地官員請吃穿山甲","createTime":"2017-02-07T00:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T04:15:40.000Z","uid":81228,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae59b04df7f24de94d1b75e6798b44a7c14f36c3","tid":110646,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T00:00:14.000Z","msg":"一條自爆被內地官員請吃珍稀野生動物穿山甲的微博今日引起廣泛關注。微博名為Ah_cal的男子曾於2015年7月15日發微博稱，自己在廣西考察期間被當地官員宴請吃國家二級保護動物穿山甲。有傳請吃的官員屬廣西投資促進局，今日下午該局有人否認相關說法。另有指這名微博主是香港一間鐘錶行的太子爺。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170206_PN_%E5%90%83%E7%A9%BF%E5%B1%B1%E7%94%B22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170206_PN_%25E5%2590%2583%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%2594%25B22.jpg&h=4c021121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片<br />\n <br />\n名為@Ah_cal的微博主曾於2015年7月15日發微博稱，自己在廣西考察期間，在當地「李局長」、「黃書記」的宴請下品嘗穿山甲。他形容：「第一次吃，口感味道很好，已經深深的愛上這野味！14號文匯報有報道！」此貼文在網上引發熱議。<br />\n <br />\n該名微博主的更多貼文一併被挖出，顯示他年紀輕輕就似乎和內地高官關係匪淺，不但享用珍稀動物穿山甲，還喝內部專供的茅台酒，搭飛機可以進入駕駛艙。網友議論紛紛，批評他炫耀特權、違規違法。目前該微博主已刪去所有微博。<br />\n <br />\n另外有傳媒爆料稱，這名微博主姓李，乃香港一間鐘錶行的太子爺，經常到內地參加招商引資團活動，並在在社交網上炫耀與當地官員吃喝的照片。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170206_PN_%E5%90%83%E7%A9%BF%E5%B1%B1%E7%94%B23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170206_PN_%25E5%2590%2583%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%2594%25B23.jpg&h=80a811bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自稱和當地高官合照。（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170206_PN_%E5%90%83%E7%A9%BF%E5%B1%B1%E7%94%B21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170206_PN_%25E5%2590%2583%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%2594%25B21.jpg&h=c28d16c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內供茅台酒。（網上圖片）<br />\n <br />\n事件除了在民間引起軒然大波，更驚動官方。內地傳媒採訪得知，廣西自治區林業廳辦公室已收到國家林業局的通知，督促其進行調查，具體調查事務由自治區森林公安局負責。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170206_PN_%E5%90%83%E7%A9%BF%E5%B1%B1%E7%94%B2-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170206_PN_%25E5%2590%2583%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%2594%25B2-1.jpg&h=45e8f8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片<br />\n <br />\n網上更有傳言稱，微博中提到的「黃書記」為廣西投資促進局的現任黨組書記黃文標。今日下午，廣西投資促進局負責宣傳工作的黎姓處長以及辦公室一位蘇姓主任回應內地傳媒，否認相關說法。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/6-%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%96%E9%87%8E/1781133-%E7%96%91%E6%B8%AF%E9%8C%B6%E8%A1%8C%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%88%BA%E7%82%AB%E8%80%80%E9%A3%AF%E5%B1%80-%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E8%AB%8B%E5%90%83%E7%A9%BF%E5%B1%B1%E7%94%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F6-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%2587%258E%2F1781133-%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%258C%25B6%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%2588%25BA%25E7%2582%25AB%25E8%2580%2580%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%2590%2583%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%2594%25B2&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=ae73d21c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/6-%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%96%E9%87%8E/1781133-%E7%96%91%E6%B8%AF%E9%8C%B6%E8%A1%8C%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%88%BA%E7%82%AB%E8%80%80%E9%A3%AF%E5%B1%80-%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E8%AB%8B%E5%90%83%E7%A9%BF%E5%B1%B1%E7%94%B2</a>"},{"pid":"b7d4b34d9e77a34a6bd8f5745de5fe96eb1a45f6","tid":110646,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T00:06:08.000Z","msg":"幫佢推下"},{"pid":"0913ce86945fc728cbc0ddc20cd51a6aaec85c14","tid":110646,"uid"